    <div class="how-it-works mb-8">
      <p class="mono text-xs mb-4" style="color: rgba(210,170,110,0.35); letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;">Rules of the pick</p>
      <div class="how-steps">
        <div class="how-step">
          <span class="how-num">→</span>
          <div>
            <p class="how-body">Your team list is ranked by position — team #1 beats team #2 if both have games tonight.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-step">
          <span class="how-num">→</span>
          <div>
            <p class="how-body">If two of your teams play each other, the game shows up once at the higher-priority team's slot.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-step">
          <span class="how-num">→</span>
          <div>
            <p class="how-body">Only evening games (5 PM – 11:30 PM your time) count. Afternoon matinees are skipped.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="how-step">
          <span class="how-num">→</span>
          <div>
            <p class="how-body">Your picks are saved in your browser — no account needed.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

